hanced diffusion\nsuppression keeping in mind the scaling of the dimensions of silicon integrated\nmicrocircuits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 May 2011 16:40:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-05-24"}
