eterminantal and\npermanental processes. More generally, we show that point processes $dcx$\nsmaller than homogeneous Poisson processes exhibit phase transitions in certain\npercolation models based on the level-sets of additive shot-noise fields, as\ne.g. $k$-percolation and SINR-percolation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 May 2011 21:50:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2011 17:48:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
